main event: An object fell into the backyard of a private dwelling in San Gabriel, California, leading to an investigation by Army explosives specialists.
interesting points: The homeowners did not witness the object fall but heard a loud thump prior to the investigation,Army personnel excavated the area in search of the object, reaching depths of up to 20 feet without finding anything,The investigation suggested the hole might have been caused by a meteorite or a missile,Authorities noted the area was once an ancient Indian village and found pottery fragments nearby.
sighted object: Unknown object that created a hole in the ground
witness description: Homeowner heard a loud thump in the backyard, but did not see the object fall.
